Title: Economic
Description: The criterion relates to the economic or financial standing of the tenderer.

Title: Technical
Description: The criterion relates to the technical or professional ability of the tenderer.

Title: Suitability
Description: The criterion relates to the suitability of the tenderer (e.g. enrolment in trade register or membership of professional organization).

Title: Other
Description: The criterion relates to other aspects of the tenderer.
